---
description: Card UI component rules
globs: ["src/components/**/*Card.tsx", "src/pages/**/*Card.tsx"]
alwaysApply: true
---

- Base: `rounded-xl bg-white p-4 border border-primary/24 border-[1px]`
- No drop shadows (`shadow-*`)
- Use `space-y-4` or `gap-4` for internal layout
- Titles: `text-lg font-medium text-primary`
- Body: `text-base text-gray-700`
- Hover: `hover:border-[#7896CA]`
